com.interpss.opf

Interface OpfGenBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBus, BaseAclfBus<AclfGen,AclfLoad>, BaseOpfBus, Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OpfBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpfGenBusImpl

    public interface OpfGenBus
extends OpfBus
    A representation of the model object 'Gen Bus'. OPF Gen Bus class for OPF analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Operating Mode
    • Inc Cost
    • Constraints
    See Also:
    OpfPackage.getOpfGenBus()
